&lt;li&gt;Conduct mock interviews (ML System Design, Coding) with actionable feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide 1:1 mentorship on career transitions and interview prep&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Host cohort orientations to drive engagement and set expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B. Curriculum Development &amp;amp; Review&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end curriculum for Agentic AI/ML (content, assignments, projects)&lt;/li&gt;
